data.description: Stunning Farmhouse in Bremond, Tx! Come see this fully renovated farmhouse nestled in a "Friday Night Lights" kind of town! It's truly a must-see property. Coffee drinkers can take their pick from 1 of 3 porches to relax on. Features include beautiful landscaping with pea gravel, gorgeous trees, solar powered accent lighting along the entire perimeter fence, quality cabinetry & charming accents throughout. The home has all new flooring and tasteful new paint that creates great ambience. The kitchen is open concept and pairs with a breakfast room & second living room. Rooms are generously-sized and windows offer fantastic natural lighting throughout. Home also has a brand-new metal framed 24'X24' garage, and a secret tool shed/workshop located...well, that's a secret (ask for photo).
